                            <comment id="13832030" author="totof3110" created="Mon, 25 Nov 2013 23:01:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Workaround is to manually exclude the dependency:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;		&amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
			&amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.apache.cxf&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
			&amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;cxf-rt-rs-security-oauth2&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
			&amp;lt;version&amp;gt;${org.apache.cxf-version}&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
			&amp;lt;exclusions&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
				&amp;lt;exclusion&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
					&amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;geronimo-servlet_3.0_spec&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
					&amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.apache.geronimo.specs&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
				&amp;lt;/exclusion&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
			&amp;lt;/exclusions&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
		&amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13832770" author="totof3110" created="Tue, 26 Nov 2013 17:17:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Saw the change in &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/cxf/trunk/rt/rs/security/oauth-parent/oauth2/pom.xml&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/cxf/trunk/rt/rs/security/oauth-parent/oauth2/pom.xml&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
